@token =  


### 1. LOGIN (Para obtener el token)
### REGISTRO DE BARBERO (para desarrollo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register-barbero
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Neman2",
    "email": "Neman2@barberia.com",
